lead_paragraph: A Dallas County grand jury is expected to indict former NFL quarterback Johnny Manziel on Tuesday on a charge of misdemeanor assault with bodily injury after he allegedly struck his ex-girlfriend, Manziel's lawyer said.

headline.print_headline: Dallas Grand Jury to Indict Former Quarterback Johnny Manziel: Lawyer
